00:41:14,710 --> 00:41:17,040
timber to build our houses...
用来建造房屋的木材

720
00:41:17,820 --> 00:41:22,270
and the rock foundations of our mighty skyscrapers.
以及我们非凡的摩天大楼的岩石地基

