00:41:25,480 --> 00:41:29,720
Over billions of years,the land that was to become the U.S.A.
几十亿年以来  美国所在的土地中

722
00:41:29,730 --> 00:41:33,250
Was endowed with greater geological riches
蕴藏着的地质宝藏

